docs.lead_paragraph: The United States Mail steamer Crescent City, Lieut J. F. SCHENCK, U. S. N. commanding, left New-Orleans, at 9.30 A. M. of the 26th ult, for New-York vid Havana, whence she sailed at 9 A. M. of the 1st instant., with the mail and passengers for this port.
